          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SI",
                "SILI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The detector system CACTUS, contains of",
                "eight Si delta-E-E telescopes. The thickness of the",
                "front and end detectors were thickness 140 and 3000 mum",
                "respectively."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The gamma-rays were detected in 28 collimated",
                " 5\"*5\" NAI(Tl) detector array, having a resolution of",
                "approx. 6% at gamma energy 1.3 MeV and a total",
                "efficiency of approx. 15%."
              ]
            },
